Laura, world linguist and archaeologist. She had a happy family when she was a child, but that all changed after an accident. Her father's obsession with the legend of immortality caused him to lose his reputation and even betray his family, and as a child Laura couldn't understand what he was doing. With the passage of time, Laura has traveled through the Evil Horse Terrace, witnessed Bermuda, Cortez after the Lost City. She now understands that what her father said could be true. In order to complete her father's research and clear his name, Laura decides to travel alone to an uncharted island on the northwestern border of Indonesia to discover the truth of what happened.
